Reset your Song-A-Week password
===============================

Someone (hopefully you) has requested a password reset for the Song-A-Week
(songs.0-z-0.com) account associated with this email address.

If this was you, and you wish to reset your password, follow this link and
choose a new password on the page:
<%= link_to reset_path(token: @user.reset_token, only_path: false), reset_path(token: @user.reset_token, only_path: false) %>

If you didn't request this password reset, simply ignore this email
and nothing will happen.

If you have any questions, you can email Travis the site administrator directly at audiodude@gmail.com.
